high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the left.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pot on the second shelf, shut the fridge door and then take the pot out again.
Turn around and head to the table.
Put the pot on the table to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter then turn right and go to the stove and turn left to face the stove
Pick up the pot from the back left burner of the stove
Turn left and go towards the door then turn left and go past the table to the fridge
Put the pot in the fridge to chill then take the pot out of the fridge
Turn around and make your way to the table
Put the pot on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the table

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the counter and walk to the white stove on the left.
Pick up the silver dish from the back left corner of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge ahead.
Put the dish inside the fridge on the second shelf, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the doors.
Turn around and walk to the white table on the right side.
Put the chilled dish to the right of the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled dish on a table.
